{
  "folder": "wfo1b78X1ygRgdoN",
  "name": "Outfit - Urban Flash (G&C Ver)",
  "type": "clothing",
  "img": "systems/cyberpunk-red-core/icons/compendium/default/Default_Clothing.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The bread-and-butter of the edgerunning community. Urban Flash outfits are usually made-to-order, produced at Night Markets for the chrome-jocks who order them. Their styles vary as widely as their wearers, but getting your hands on one of these is a rite of passage - if you're wearing one, you've made it. Often feature personal logos or insignias, or incorporate designs from the wearer's past or dream future.</p><ul><li><p>Can be sourced by any fixer or found at any Night Market.</p></li><li><p>After being bought, the user declares what type of outfit it is they've purchased, from the table below. </p><ul><li><p>Select the relevant effect from the effects tab, and delete the remainder. </p></li><li><p>Sub-skills (science, martial art, local expert) are also selected at the time of purchase.</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Once a week while being worn, the user gains <strong>the associated benefits from their chosen table entry</strong> for 12 hours. </p></li><li><p>Characters can only benefit from one outfit's provided bonuses at a time.</p></li></ul><table><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"100\"><p>Outfit Type</p></td><td><p>Bonuses (+1 per skill)</p></td><td><p>Description</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"100\"><p>Phantom's Flexweave</p></td><td><p>Stealth, Contortionist, Pick Lock, Pick Pocket, Conceal/Reveal Object</p></td><td><p>Dark fabrics to absorb light and hide movement - fits well over a bodyweight suit.</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"100\"><p>Wrecker's Weave</p></td><td><p>Brawling, Autofire, Heavy Weapons</p></td><td><p>Big, bulky sleeves and deep pockets for holding big ammo and big arms, be they flesh or metal.</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"100\"><p>Tactician's Threads</p></td><td><p>Concentration, Tactics, Deduction, Demolitions, 1 science skill the user already knows</p></td><td><p>Sleek techwear, with a small array of built-in tools designed to help the wearer command a battlefield.</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"100\"><p>Whirlwind's Weave</p></td><td><p>Athletics, 1 Martial Art the user already knows, Handgun, Archery</p></td><td><p>Wind-resistant, flashy clothing designed to compliment the user's quick feet and quick thinking.</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"100\"><p>Broker's Blazer</p></td><td><p>1 Local Expert area, Gamble, Streetwise, Bribery, Forgery</p></td><td><p>The perfect suit for dealing on the streets - totally unique, dripping with the local culture, lending credibility when it counts.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>"
    },
